Johannesburg - Aishwarya Kumar takes to the streets of Rosebank to find out why this up and coming neighbourhood is becoming the ‘it spot’ for tourists in Johannesburg. The Rosebank Art & Craft Market, the Sunday market, the mall combined with a prime locality with Gautrain, buses and tuk tuk readily available, tourists and locals love to bring their family and friends for a laid-back day. IOL  